{"tid":301864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺南究竟咩事 玩弄莘莘學子","createTime":"2017-06-29T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T03:37:41.000Z","uid":67091,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2808965988bc77a0a24604a6171d679b678ed6b8","tid":301864,"uid":67091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"我呢讀書一向好差 好hea，努力左兩年asso都叫有3.2，但無八大比interview我，鬼叫我廢咩。<br />\n<br />\n上個星期，lingu 比左個運動員獎學金計劃，佢份from又叫你重新揀3個系，又問你係咪經nonju報，我以為機會黎啦，可以申請獎學金加入學。<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個街，之後佢打黎叫我去in，我問in邊科，佢竟然話吾同，我比獎學金你，唔代表有offer，wtf ，我唔係你學生你竟然叫我去申請獎學金？張from 又搞到好似入學from咁，之後同我講唔係比你入學啊廢柴，咁你點解唔check下我係咪你學生先呢？<br />\n<br />\n大佬，30號就係，我去左係咪會比佢羞辱，有無人知佢咁大間學校係咩玩法？？？"},{"pid":"0d3aafaa2d2461d8ddc07fc38444ca5807a3e25d","tid":301864,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"你係講呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ln.edu.hk/ssc/sports/athletes-scholarships/Chi_ES_form_2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ln.edu.hk%2Fssc%2Fsports%2Fathletes-scholarships%2FChi_ES_form_2017.pdf&d=O6IRHH6heEBx9e2wK3qu4TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6821ee7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ln.edu.hk/ssc/sports/athletes-scholarships/Chi_ES_form_2017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗係佢寫得衰，搞到你誤會左，個野似乎係比你報大學果陣順手報埋，唔係用埋報大學。因為正常non jupas 報u 應該唔係填果份咁簡單既表就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於表入面果三格，係問你報左啲咩科，唔係比你揀。。。"},{"pid":"70580e8b57548e59beb2d13251f211d77885d021","tid":301864,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"不過, 我都唔太肯定，不如你打去問下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\